ce share awards granted are expensed over the three-year requisite performance and service period. Awards shall become", "bbox": [93.5, 948.1, 1149.7, 970.8]}, {"text": "vested if (1) the Company achieves certain specified stock performance targets compared to a defined group of peer companies", "bbox": [93.5, 972.7, 1149.8, 995.4]}, {"text": "and (2) the employee remains continuously employed by the company during the performance period.  Partial vesting may occur", "bbox": [93.5, 997.4, 1149.9, 1020.1]}, {"text": "after separation from service in the case of certain terminations not for cause and for retirements.", "bbox": [93.5, 1022.0, 889.4, 1044.7]}, {"text": "In 2015, 2014, and 2013, the Company issued performance shares covering 61,611, 58,206, and 47,032 shares, respectively. The", "bbox": [93.5, 1071.2, 1149.7, 1094.0]}, {"text": "performance share awards granted in 2014 and 2015 are considered performance condition awards as attainment is based on", "bbox": [93.5, 1095.9, 1149.9, 1118.6]}, {"text": "Dover's performance relative to established internal metrics. The fair value of these awards was determined using Dover's closing", "bbox": [93.5, 1120.5, 1149.6, 1143.2]}, {"text": "stock price on the date of grant. The expected attainment of the internal metrics for these awards is analyzed each reporting period,", "bbox": [93.5, 1145.1, 1149.6, 1167.9]}, {"text": "and the related expense is adjusted up or down based on expected attainment, if that attainment differs from previous estimates.", "bbox": [93.5, 1169.8, 1149.6, 1192.5]}, {"text": "The cumulative effect on current and prior periods of a change in attainment is recognized in compensation cost in the period of", "bbox": [93.5, 1194.4, 1149.7, 1217.1]}, {"text": "change.", "bbox": [93.5, 1219.0, 161.9, 1241.7]}, {"text": "The fair value and average attainment used in determining compensation cost of the performance shares issued in 2014 and 2015", "bbox": [93.5, 1268.3, 1155.0, 1291.0]}, {"text": "is as follows for the year ended December 31, 2015:", "bbox": [93.5, 1292.9, 522.2, 1315.6]}, {"text": "Performance shares", "bbox": [941.2, 1333.6, 1116.2, 1356.3]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [949.5, 1362.2, 990.5, 1385.0]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1065.5, 1362.2, 1106.5, 1385.0]}, {"text": "Fair value per share at date of grant", "bbox": [99.7, 1389.2, 391.0, 1412.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [922.9, 1389.2, 933.1, 1412.0]}, {"text": "73.28", "bbox": [960.1, 1389.2, 1006.3, 1412.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1037.8, 1389.2, 1048.1, 1412.0]}, {"text": "82.51", "bbox": [1077.1, 1389.2, 1123.3, 1412.0]}, {"text": "Average attainment rate reflected in expense", "bbox": [99.7, 1415.9, 466.3, 1438.7]}, {"text": "11.98%", "bbox": [960.1, 1415.9, 1023.4, 1438.7]}, {"text": "34.33%", "bbox": [1077.2, 1415.9, 1140.4, 1438.7]}, {"text": "The performance share awards granted in 2013 are market condition awards as attainment is based on Dover's three-year", "bbox": [93.5, 1471.5, 1149.8, 1494.2]}, {"text": "performance relative to its peer group for the relevant performance period. These awards were valued on the date of grant using", "bbox": [93.5, 1496.1, 1149.7, 1518.8]}]}